      "role": "user",
      "content": "ok that makes sense for the economic side. but can you go deeper into the \"cultural preservation\" aspect? like, what were the specific arguments made about how segregation helped maintain the distinct traditions, values, or social structures of different racial groups? i need to understand the logic they used to claim it was actually BENEFICIAL for those communities to be separate.",
